---
title: Mediterranean-Style Beef Bowl with Couscous, Mint & Ocean Spray Craisins
description: How satisfying is saucy beef mince on a bed of fluffy couscous that's smattered with Ocean Spray Craisins® 50% Less Sugar Dried
Cranberries? You'll have to make this delectable Mediterranean-inspired dish to find out! We've added cooling yoghurt and refreshing
mint to top it off. Simply delicious.
